      • fix

        @NotNull
public static @NotNull var fix(@Nullable
                                        @Nullable var v,
                                        int depth,
                                        boolean parallel)
        Fix, i.e. evaluate lambdas to the depth supplied, optionally hinting that parallel behaviour is fine
        Parameters:
        v - the object to be fixed
        depth - the depth at which to stop evaluation, 1 means do not penetrate any layers of maps/blocks, 2 means penetrate one layer of maps.
        parallel - if true parallel evaluation if fine
        Returns:
        the 'fixed' var
